WEBVTT

00:08.475 --> 00:12.350
This week on "VICE," the
new space race to Mars.

00:14.058 --> 00:17.682
The key to rapid
innovation is competition.

00:17.683 --> 00:20.224
It's a really exciting
time to be in space.

00:20.225 --> 00:21.892
Man: You have about 15
to 20 more seconds.

00:27.067 --> 00:30.666
And then, the legacy of the
prison camp at Guantanamo Bay.

00:31.267 --> 00:33.824
Gianna Toboni: You were
the guy that was assigned

00:33.825 --> 00:35.074
to create this place.

00:35.075 --> 00:37.407
If you could say one
thing to the detainees

00:37.408 --> 00:39.366
who were innocent,
what would you say?

00:39.367 --> 00:41.824
It's time for America
to shut it down.

